betterquesting.name: Wood Age
betterquesting.desc: A new age dawns before you! You don't have anything to work with but this tree, so let's make the most of it!

betterquesting.name: Stone Age
betterquesting.desc: Now that you have a good source of blocks, it's time to expand, upgrade, and improve your island a bit!

betterquesting.name: Farming Age
betterquesting.desc: Time to fight back against this cold, empty void, and grow some things!

betterquesting.name: Mystical Farming
betterquesting.desc: Resources are finite, but crops will grow whatever you need.

betterquesting.name: Age of Exploration
betterquesting.desc: With the right tools you no longer have to be confined to your small island. Time to get out and stretch our legs! Try not to die...

betterquesting.name: Age of Machines
betterquesting.desc: Your skill with technology is growing. Automation is key.

betterquesting.name: Age of Power
betterquesting.desc: Once you start on this path, how much is enough?

betterquesting.name: Green Energy
betterquesting.desc: Free, renewable energy!

betterquesting.name: Age of Enhancement
betterquesting.desc: Your tools are not powerful enough, time for an upgrade.

betterquesting.name: Alchemic Wizardry
Age of the Botanist
Mastery
Age of Dragons
betterquesting.desc: You will be tested. It takes a legend to conquer legends.

betterquesting.name: Age of the Traveler

betterquesting.name: Age of Insanity
